Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Dalig Elementary School in the Municipality of Balayan, Province of Batangas, to Doña Margarita Toribio Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 779
An Act Changing the Name of the Dalig Elementary School in the Municipality of Balayan, Province of Batangas, to Doña Margarita Toribio Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Dalig Elementary School in the Municipality of Balayan, Province of Batangas, is changed to Doña Margarita Toribio Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
